s=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614213\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kth1665702687631.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kth1665702687631.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kth1665702687631.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kth1665702687631\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Header Text Color (HeaderTextColor) \n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Color to use as the foreground color of grid widget headers.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kth1665702687631__p_d104468e1_d104469e1_d104470e1\">HeaderColor<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> |\n        <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">RGBColor</var></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                     information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a\n                     color. For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">#D90E1A</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__1\">RGBColor</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kth1665702687631__table_d12335e1_d12336e1_d12337e1__entry__2\">RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form\n                        <var class=\"keyword varname\">R</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">G</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">B</var>.\n                     For example <code class=\"ph codeph\">255,0,0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kth1665702687631__section_yr2_p3c_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479780e136\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"clg1695282025414.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" title=\"The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.\">egrid (Grid)</a></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kth1665702687631__section_ug5_p3c_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479780e153\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kth1665702687631__p_d104480e1_d104481e1_d104482e1\">Uniface follows Windows behavior in applying colors.\n        Depending on the Windows version and the object, the color may not always be applied.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kth1665702687631__p_d104483e1_d104484e1_d104485e1\">To provide a consistent appearance no matter what\n        version of Windows is being used, the default background and foreground colors of the grid\n        widget are defined using HeaderColor and HeaderTextColor properties in the\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kth1665702687631__p_d104486e1_d104487e1_d104488e1\">The HeaderTextColor property enables you to adjust the\n        text color if you choose a dark color for HeaderColor.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kth1665702687631__section_rbd_r3c_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479780e171\">Setting Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kth1665702687631__p_d104492e1_d104493e1_d104494e1\">The HeaderColor and HeaderTextColor properties can be\n        set in <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>, in the More properties of the Grid Widget properties\n        dialog, and in ProcScript using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entityProperties</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kth1665702687631__pre_igs_s3c_xwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putitem/id vProperties,\"HeaderColor\",\"ControlLight\";\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"HeaderTextColor\",\"green\"\n$entityproperties(ORDERLINE.SALES)=vProperties</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sqz1665702687558.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Header Color (HeaderColor)</a><p>Color to use as the background of grid widget headers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ihz1665702686784.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Column Headers</a><p>This property determines whether column headers are displayed. True (default) or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdz1665702687413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Row Numbering</a><p>This property determines whether row numbers are displayed if Row Headers is enabled. True or False (default).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614213\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614213\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Header Text Color (HeaderTextColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Header Text Color (HeaderTextColor) Color to use as the foreground color of grid widget headers. HeaderColor = ColorName | HexColorNumber | RGBColor Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic. HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. For example: #D90E1A . RGBColor RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form R , G , B . For example 255,0,0 Applies To egrid (Grid) Description Uniface follows Windows behavior in applying colors. Depending on the Windows version and the object, the color may not always be applied. To provide a consistent appearance no matter what version of Windows is being used, the default background and foreground colors of the grid widget are defined using HeaderColor and HeaderTextColor properties in the usys.ini . The HeaderTextColor property enables you to adjust the text color if you choose a dark color for HeaderColor. Setting Properties The HeaderColor and HeaderTextColor properties can be set in usys.ini , in the More properties of the Grid Widget properties dialog, and in ProcScript using $entityProperties . putitem/id vProperties,\"HeaderColor\",\"ControlLight\";\" putitem/id vProperties,\"HeaderTextColor\",\"green\" $entityproperties(ORDERLINE.SALES)=vProperties Copy Related Links Header Color (HeaderColor) Color to use as the background of grid widget headers. Column Headers This property determines whether column headers are displayed. True (default) or False. Row Numbering This property determines whether row numbers are displayed if Row Headers is enabled. True or False (default). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}